### Test server
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Register a user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sethum",
  "email": "sethumdamsavi1@gmail.com",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sethumdamsavi1@gmail.com",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### Get all charities
GET http://localhost:5000/api/charities

### Create a charity
POST http://localhost:5000/api/charities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Children Education Fund",
  "description": "Helping underprivileged children access education in Sri Lanka",
  "target": 500000
}

### Get charity by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/charities/1

### Follow a charity
POST http://localhost:5000/api/charities/1/follow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1
}

### Create online donation
POST http://localhost:5000/api/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "userId": 1,
  "charityId": 1
}

### Get donations for user
GET http://localhost:5000/api/donations/user/1

### Get donations for charity
GET http://localhost:5000/api/donations/charity/1

### Submit offline donation
POST http://localhost:5000/api/donations/offline
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 10000,
  "userId": 1,
  "charityId": 1
}

### Approve donation (admin)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/donations/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "approved"
}